Package: kitty
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: the fast, feature-rich, cross-platform, GPU based terminal.
 kitty is designed for power keyboard users. To that end all its controls work with the keyboard.
 Its configuration is a simple, human editable, single file for easy reproducibility.
